Class Question

java.lang.Object
Question
public class Question extends Object
The Question class serves as a representation of the quetions that will be populated into the quiz GUI panels. It will take the question body, correct anwers, and incorrect answers and provide ways to jumble them and keep track of the answer.

    • generateRandomOrder

      public void generateRandomOrder()
      The generateRandomOrder() method generates the scrambledOutput String Array by randomly assigning items from both the answers and nonAnswers array into the scrambledOutput array. It saves the indexes of the correct answers into the correctAnswerIndexes array.
